sectionNotes: Restricted to BSLAS: Earth,Soc,Env Sust-UIUC or BSLAS: ESES Online - UIUC.
sectionText: This section is restricted ONLINE undergraduate students pursuing the bachelor's degree in Earth, Society and Environmental Sustainability or the online ENSU certificate.. There are weekly assignments with due dates but no specific meeting time. If all seats are full, complete the form at http://go.illinois.edu/NRESwaitinglist to be added to the waiting list.
